    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247510/extras/c83df7033ea7a956c91b3e912b9c06bb.poster.avif?t=1730035075\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247510/extras/c83df7033ea7a956c91b3e912b9c06bb.webm?t=1730035075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247510/extras/c83df7033ea7a956c91b3e912b9c06bb.mp4?t=1730035075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >希勃宇宙空间站遭遇了诡异事件，所有机组人员被迫紧急撤离。你必须深入险地查明站内状况，并使出浑身解数扭转乾坤。行径古怪的人工智能主管，充满敌意的机械化工作人员，幽光缠绕的走廊内，一闪而过的黑影……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >情况正在持续恶化</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247510/extras/fd2f645aba9a5643739d0a2c8e19e9e6.avif?t=1730035075\" width=588 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用自身技能突袭、封锁、毁灭你的敌人。无论是枪弹轰击还是近身肉搏，放轻脚步隐匿身形，潜入希勃空间站深处。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247510/extras/efe055604d0022e1f7950cf27b7bbdf3.avif?t=1730035075\" width=588 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >弹药所剩无几，急救包和其他物资储备告急。升级变得更加艰难，敌人却愈发棘手——唯有最强者才能在绝境中撑起一片苍穹！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247510/extras/c6307dda1325a46006d6a903a8f9a167.avif?t=1730035075\" width=588 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >音乐动态和空间音频系统令无惧的勇士也毛骨悚然。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247510/extras/d45684824f96732c19b3e1e5a6caf15f.avif?t=1730035075\" width=588 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >NanoCatastrophe 将持续支持你找寻出路与解决方案。其中的某些发现会使你欣喜若狂受益良多，而某些，则会招致无尽的苦难。</p>",
